Purpose
Decompose high-level requirements into actionable deliverables.

Inputs

Feature description
Business goals
Constraints

Prompt

Act as a senior Business Analyst.

Break down the following feature into detailed requirements:
{feature_description}

Ensure:
1. Functional and non-functional requirements are separated
2. Requirements are atomic and testable
3. Dependencies between requirements are identified
4. Each requirement includes rationale

Also classify:
- Priority (High/Medium/Low)
- Complexity (Simple/Moderate/Complex)

Outputs

Functional requirements
Non-functional requirements
Priority & complexity
Dependencies
